{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;All materials used in this page description were created only from the demo version.&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/EN_01.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/KakaoTalk_20241022_165350328__\uc0ac\uc6a9\uc790_\uc9c0\uc815_.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Does that shape look like a hexagon to you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Hexagon.gif?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shine light to reveal its true form.<strong><br><br>\u201cTHANKS, LIGHT. - DEMO\u201d</strong> is curated with puzzles that let anyone quickly learn THANKS, LIGHT. from the main game, while gradually offering more intriguing challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try a few stages from Chapter 1, explore the early part of the story, and look for hidden elements in between.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Line.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/EN_03.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Lighting.gif?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u201cTHANKS, LIGHT - DEMO\u201d</strong> is a puzzle platformer where you shine or absorb light to transform objects between 2D and 3D states.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don\u2019t judge objects by their silhouettes. Shine light to discover their real shape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Line.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/EN_04.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Rotation.gif?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Did you know that even cylinders can contain squares?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the hidden shapes within each figure and solve parts of the puzzles in ways only possible in <strong>\u201cTHANKS, LIGHT - DEMO.\u201d</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Line.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/EN_05.png?t=1737619596\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Physics.gif?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the 2D state, there is no physics,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">but in the 3D state, physics applies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use this characteristic to traverse between two and three dimensions and solve various physics puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Line.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/EN_06.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Story.gif?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the mysterious space prepared by the self-proclaimed \u2018Administrator,\u2019</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">explore and uncover hidden events.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737619596","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/page.bg.jpg?t=1737619596","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/1d7b17bf62a51e16cd71576e300df7474dd42217/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737619596","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/1d7b17bf62a51e16cd71576e300df7474dd42217/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737619596","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;All materials used in this page description were created only from the demo version.&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/EN_01.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/KakaoTalk_20241022_165350328__\uc0ac\uc6a9\uc790_\uc9c0\uc815_.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Does that shape look like a hexagon to you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamst