res?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the hidden shapes within each figure and solve parts of the puzzles in ways only possible in <strong>\u201cTHANKS, LIGHT - DEMO.\u201d</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Line.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/EN_05.png?t=1737619596\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Physics.gif?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the 2D state, there is no physics,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">but in the 3D state, physics applies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use this characteristic to traverse between two and three dimensions and solve various physics puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Line.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/EN_06.png?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276550/extras/Story.gif?t=1737619596\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the mysterious space prepared by the self-proclaimed \u2018Administrator,\u2019</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">explore and uncover hidden events.</p>","developers":["Lighters"],"fullgame":{"appid":"2544740","name":"THANKS, LIGHT."},"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse